        properties:
            locator: "Sansa IV"
            text_from_source: "The boy clawed at his throat, his face black, his legs jerking. 'He's choking,' Queen Margaery gasped."
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "The Purple Wedding. King Joffrey is poisoned with the Strangler at his wedding feast. Tyrion is accused. Sansa flees King's Landing with Ser Dontos."
